      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "A well-kept classic with plenty of vintage charm and a strong, honest presence. This is a good driver-quality car that presents nicely, shows well overall, and feels ready to enjoy right away. It\u2019s not a show car, but it has the kind of clean, appealing condition and character that make it easy to be proud of and have fun with.",
