      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Presentable, practical, and priced right, this fair-condition car still has plenty to offer as a dependable everyday driver. It shows normal cosmetic wear and age-related use, but overall it comes across well and delivers good value for someone who wants affordable, usable transportation without overspending. A solid budget-conscious option with honest everyday appeal.",
