    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy runabout, or a great little project to make their own. Priced fairly for what it is, and offered by a seller who believes in being straight with people. If you want something inexpensive, usable, and full of potential, this one is well worth a look.",
